{"tid":1790943,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發]YouTube戰線要人","createTime":"2019-12-20T11:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T11:29:02.000Z","uid":28942,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"026d145578cbc3e00daf017b07055fc7b6c72be2","tid":1790943,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"話說呢個YouTuber我不嬲都有follow開，佢嘅節目非常高質周圍飛去唔同嘅地方去食嘢。<br />\n佢啱啱upload咗條片係佢去咗香港，雖然有八成嘅時間都係講大排檔，但係佢都有講到關於香港反送中示威嘅事情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xN75_QQODLw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxN75_QQODLw&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5UpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=5df7a171\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xN75_QQODLw</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然佢冇實際講到啲乜嘢，但係聽佢口吻佢係支持呢一場運動。<br />\n<br />\n最重要係咩，佢有超過3百萬個subscribers!!<br />\nYouTube嘅旅遊節目入邊佢排第五!<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位手足入去留一留言，例如<br />\nThank you so much for coming to Hong Kong! We are sorry that you encountered a road block, but we are fighting for our freedom and democracy. <br />\nYou are forever welcome to come to our beautiful city!<br />\n<br />\nWe are fighting for our freedom and right so people around the globe can continue to have these amazing food in Hong Kong, freely!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7825b33eebf8bbbfe8bc54b98faf1846f3885018","tid":1790943,"uid":28942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"佢啲片勁高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f2255da6c17bb9182f4891a82827789febaa38","tid":1790943,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:18:06.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c594ab31eccf229d73850bcec17d68e3e8673bd","tid":1790943,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:18:27.000Z","msg":"大家去留言之餘，麻煩like下其他手足嘅留言。推佢上去！"},{"pid":"bce655ac153cfc26211f55a250154c71d99f623b","tid":1790943,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38e8b3ce94f154b5d3426e0bd04b0650c868bf9f","tid":1790943,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:19:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢係YouTube旅遊Channel入邊排第五架各位！</span>"},{"pid":"888420e3d1a92a617e684e931da6e30a12548ce6","tid":1790943,"uid":28942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:19:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">傳播力不容忽視</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"677fb74d8caf03eae6a61f6a8f9a3c2587ee90b2","tid":1790943,"uid":316241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:21:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"434c9183d3ead421c0debb6923781028f0286493","tid":1790943,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"d324b9d5d1d27edaaf1e1d1e85594a18d687d573","tid":1790943,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:23:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxv